00:49:21.810 --> 00:49:23.976
I don't know the answer but
it'd be a great question

00:49:23.976 --> 00:49:25.580
to study which is,
could we correlate

00:49:25.580 --> 00:49:27.970
some of these
differences in language

00:49:27.970 --> 00:49:29.280
with societal inequality?

00:49:29.280 --> 00:49:31.529
I mean, this
