00:49:31.529 --> 00:49:33.070
that only works for
places where they

00:49:33.070 --> 00:49:37.256
have menus online because
that's what I used,

00:49:37.256 --> 00:49:38.380
but that's a lot of places.

00:49:38.380 --> 00:49:39.440
Right.

00:49:39.440 --> 00:49:41.480
It's mostly the first
World but there's still

00:49:41.480 --> 00:49:42.740
inequality differences
in the First World

00:49:42.740 --> 00:49:44.140
and you could see
if they correlate

00:49:44.140 --> 00:49:44.870
with these kind of things.

00:49:44.870 --> 00:49:45.860
That would be cool.

00:49:45.860 --> 00:49:46.870
AUDIENCE: In the
